description:
Ultimate Surrender's Summer Vengeance Championship Match
This match up was a year in the making. Last time they met up the Nightmare won by 1 point in the very last second of the match.
This fight came down to the last couple of seconds with both wrestlers giving more then they had in the effort. A champion was crowned, a season is over and a amazing tournament comes to and end. Brutally Epic!
title: Posting of Aug 28th's Live Event Vendetta The Nightmare
